Welcome to the Company HR Policy Guide.

1. Leave Policy:
   Employees are entitled to 20 days of paid annual leave, excluding weekends and public holidays.

2. Remote Work:
   Employees may work remotely up to 3 days per week with manager approval.

3. Working Hours:
   Standard working hours are from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM, Monday to Friday.

4. Dress Code:
   Business casual is expected unless otherwise specified for an event.

5. Code of Conduct:
   All employees must adhere to ethical business practices and treat colleagues with respect.

For more details, contact the HR department at hr@company.com.
